  <summary date="2019-11-18T17:56:14Z" status="Introduced in House">Stadiums Operating under New Guidance Act or the SONG Act

This bill revises the authority of the Federal Aviation Administration (FAA) to issue temporary flight restrictions for sporting events.

The bill requires the FAA to revise the meaning of "sporting" to include all major events held in stadiums, including concerts.</summary>
